graph TD
    Client[Browser Frontend - Next.js App] -->|HTTPS| BFF[Next.js API Serverless Route]
    Client -->|Local Processing| Canvas[Canvas API - FloodFill/Resize]
    Client -->|Local Processing| SVG_Engine[ImageTracer.js - Vectorizer]
    BFF -->|REST/HTTPS| Gemini[Google Gemini 2.5 Flash API]
    BFF -->|REST/HTTPS| DB[(Firebase Firestore - Opcional Logs)]
    Gemini -->|Returns JSON Audit| BFF
    BFF -->|Returns Data| Client

